overview: On April 9th GCW presents Paranoid live on FITE straight from Ukrainian Cultural Center in Los Angeles, CA. The event features GCW Extreme Title Match where AJ Gray defends his title against Swerve.  Also in the lineup:  Minoru Suzuki vs Blake Christian  Bussy (Allie Kat & Effy) vs The Briscoes (Mark and Jay Briscoe)  Chris Dickinson vs Masha Slamovich  Chris Bey vs Jack Cartwheel  AJ Gray vs Kevin Blackwood  ACH vs Nick Wayne  .....and more!
title: GCW: Paranoid
